      "span_text": "Animals. C57BL/6 mice with a targeted disruption of the gene encoding STAT6 (Stat6 Ϫ / Ϫ ) were generated in the Department of Biochemistry at the Hyogo College of Medicine as previously reported [CITATION_1] , and age-and sex-matched wild-type (wt) littermate controls (C57BL/6 mice) were purchased from the Sankyo Co."
